#supportukraineğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¦ #stopwarinukraine #stopwar 

I find it super hard to concentrate and do my job these daysâ€¦My mind is constantly thinking about how to support this situation and help dear friends like @itsmekseniaschnaider stuck in their country, facing bombs, fearing for their lives. I went to #kiev 2 times and I love that welcoming creative country, full with talented designers, in this pic by @styledumonde I indeed wear a @kseniaschnaider upcycled dress made of second-hand football shirts. She has  set up info on how support the Ukranian army on her website for the â€œReturn Alive Foundationâ€

Letâ€™s not abandon them!

I share this message I got from @wr_agency so that you know what to do: 

â€œUkraine is facing an unprecedented challenge. Our brave soldiers and civilians defend not only Ukrainian land and values, but the whole Western world. 
We are on the frontline and we need your help! Please support us in our fight by donating the badly needed medical supplies!
We have organized the logistics chain that will facilitate the transfer of goods from Polandâ€™s warehouse directly to our defenders all over the country.

This initiative is supported in coordination with the Office of the President of Ukraine and Ukraineâ€™s Armed Forces

Please see www.helpukraine.center for details on what medical aid is needed and where to send!

Also visit https://unitedhelpukraine.org
how-to-help-ukraine-now.super.site/
#standwithukraine

helpukraine.center/en

On this website you can find out how to provide humanitarian assistance to the people of Ukraine.

Ukrainian businessmen have opened a warehouse to which you can send any cargo that will help people.

Today we are thinking of all the women and children of Ukraine. We will be donating 10% of all online sales to a Ukrainian recommended charity* from today until the end of March. 

On 25 March we (Brenda & Helen) will be taking part in an International Womenâ€™s Day show at Brent Civic Centre, London hosted by @handmadecardsbydayo We will also use this opportunity to raise money for a Ukrainian Charity. More details to follow. 

#iwd #internationalwomensday #women #ukraine #stopwar #standbyukraine ğŸ’™ğŸ’›

* https://helpukraine.center/

#Reakiro is grateful to everyone for their efforts and help. By working together, we have gathered the resources needed by both the Ukrainian military and those who were forced to temporarily leave their homes. 

This includes bulletproof vests, medical supplies, sleeping bags, clothes and food for adults and children. All of which were delivered to the distribution centre of volunteer assistance in Lviv, Ukraine. 

To continue your support help Ukraine - https://helpukraine.center/en

Together we stand! 
Yours #ReakiroTeam ğŸŒ±

#standwithukraine #stopwarinukraine #stopwar
